      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Rinse your <strong>brown rice</strong> and add it to a pot with plenty of <strong>cold water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat.</p><p>Once boiling reduce the heat to medium and cook for 20-25 min or until it's tender with a slight bite</p><p>Once cooked, drain and set aside</p>",
