      "instruction": "<p>Squeeze 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>lemon juice</strong> into a large mixing bowl</p><p>Combine with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and season with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> then set aside – this is your <strong>lemon dressing</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>salad </strong>and pat dry with kitchen paper, then chop it roughly</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-low heat</p>",
