    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain your <strong>jumbo</strong> <strong>prawns</strong>, then add them to the pan<strong> </strong>with your <strong>cayenne pepper</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and cook for 5-6 min or until the prawns are cooked through</p><p>Add 50ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[75ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[100ml]</span> <strong>water</strong> and cook for 1-2 min further until the tomatoes and garlic oil form a thick sauce</p><p>Once thickened, stir through the remaining<strong> chopped parsley</strong> and remove from the heat – these are your <strong>Andalusian-style jumbo prawns</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
