    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Toss your <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>salad</strong> and <strong>brown rice</strong> together in the bowl of <strong>lemon dressing </strong>– this is your <strong>brown rice salad</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon[s] </strong>into 1 wedge per person</p>",
      "order": 7,
